</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons">The Simpsons</a></em>:
<ul><li> In "<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Recap/TheSimpsonsS5E6MargeOnTheLam" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Recap/TheSimpsonsS5E6MargeOnTheLam">Marge on the Lam</a>" Ruth Powers stole her ex-husband's car since he wouldn't pay alimony. Marge's response:
<div class="indent"><strong>Marge</strong>: Didn't you realize all you had to do was report him to the police? <br><strong>Ruth</strong>: <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DidntThinkThisThrough" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DidntThinkThisThrough">Marge, you're the levelheaded friend I never had.</a>
