<ul><li> In "<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/DuckDodgersInTheTwentyFourthAndAHalfCentury" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/DuckDodgersInTheTwentyFourthAndAHalfCentury">Duck Dodgers in the 24&frac12;th Century</a>'', Dodgers shows the Space Cadet a needlessly complicated route for reaching Planet X, so complicated he doesn't even understand it himself. Cadet then suggests following a line of conveniently lettered planets, a suggestion <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladIThoughtOfIt" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GladIThoughtOfIt">Dodgers then takes as his own</a>.
