<h2 class="bold font-l">Rescuing Susie From the Bears</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Jimjams has a complicated and dangerous plan to rescue a sleepwalking Susie, but Oscar points out he could just carry her to safety. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1v1fp8" data-video-descrip="When Bitsy wants to get warm, she tells Helen to use her knife to cut herself open so she can sleep inside her. Helen tells her she's going to use the knife to pry the hinge pins from the door off so they can leave the room." data-video-title="Cut Yourself Open" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1v1fp8_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_cut_yourself_open.png" data-video-trope="Main/StatingTheSimpleSolution" data-video-tropename="Stating the Simple Solution" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/CentralParkS1E9LiveItUpTonight,WesternAnimation/CentralPark" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_cut_yourself_open.png">
<p><span class="bold">Cut Yourself Open</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="711law" data-video-descrip="When Owen's oven catches on fire and wonders how he's going to heat his pizza, Birdie points out he could just buy a pizza but Owen refuses. When Owen and Birdie takes the pizza to the forge so Jimmy can heat it using the forge, Jimmy also points out the same solution to Owen." data-video-title="You Could Buy a Pizza" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/711law_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_you_could_buy_a_pizza.png" data-video-trope="Main/StatingTheSimpleSolution" data-video-tropename="Stating the Simple Solution" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/CentralParkS1E8HotOven,WesternAnimation/CentralPark" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_you_could_buy_a_pizza.png">
<p><span class="bold">You Could Buy a...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="7lr14h" data-video-descrip="When Birdie tries to rescue Owen &amp;amp; Cole from the tree, he suggests getting one of the Macy's Thanksgiving Parade balloons (a Pikachu or Garfield) to cushion their fall. Owen just tells him to get a ladder from the park's storage shed." data-video-title="Parade Balloon Idea" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/7lr14h_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_birdie_helping.png" data-video-trope="Main/StatingTheSimpleSolution" data-video-tropename="Stating the Simple Solution" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/CentralParkS1E6RivalBusker,WesternAnimation/CentralPark" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cp_birdie_helping.png">
<p><span class="bold">Parade Balloon ...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="c14ruo" data-video-descrip="Bob and Linda's idea to block the sunlight is having Teddy hold a cardboard on the window until the sun moves. Teddy points out they could just tape to hold the cardboard on the window, but Teddy is too nice to turn down their request." data-video-title="There is Tape" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/c14ruo_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/bb_there_is_tape_3.png" data-video-trope="Main/StatingTheSimpleSolution" data-video-tropename="Stating the Simple Solution" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/BobsBurgersS10E14WagTheSong,WesternAnimation/BobsBurgers" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/bb_there_is_tape_3.png">
<p><span class="bold">There is Tape</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="221c2p" data-video-descrip="&amp;quot;So, you're saying, what I have to do to fall asleep, is GO TO SLEEP. Right? Is that what you're saying, Melissa?!&amp;quot;" data-video-title="Home Movies" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/221c2p_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/221c2p.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/StatingTheSimpleSolution" data-video-tropename="Stating the Simple Solution" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/HomeMovies" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/221c2p.jpg">
